         <p>Have an amazing project to share? Join the SHOW-AND-TELL every <a href="https://plus.google.com/u/0/b/112526208786662512291/112526208786662512291/posts" title="SHOW AND TELL" target="_blank">Wednesday night at 7:30pm ET on Google+ Hangouts.</a></p> 
